islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漁護署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3192953722910ac27a3748a6d7b376e7ab658c32","tid":670200,"uid":60219,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"我第一次睇條片都即刻諗起班蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e46e70f37efbe47af90b725460d9722c3581a23","tid":670200,"uid":143598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54941135ab379718b2dc8ee1e1273cfac770792b","tid":670200,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff27a78ae353b25f2e678739f7397cfbc32ddd32","tid":670200,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"漁記痴撚左線"},{"pid":"95eac5651d4876f5fd95c1dfc271155326c7721c","tid":670200,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪堡主d針已經入左政府"},{"pid":"25d4a62bca1b3fd4d2f34f7653372158f39fd062","tid":670200,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b424b82d7c20767f5cef00b8174a5b8347d1add0","tid":670200,"uid":184332,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"講到底有人心虛。<br />\n大自然突然大量放生本來唔好,加上有人一早踢爆放完再捉找錢,跟本個廣告是勸世,但是阻賊搵食所以比人投